STATE v. CORPENING. No. COA05-1641. North Carolina Court of Appeals. Filed September 5, 2006. Certification Date September 25, 2006. Appeal from Surry (03CRS50040, 03CRS51027).

Case reported without published opinion. No error as to the conviction for possession of cocaine (03CRS51027); Reversed as to conviction for resist, delay, and obstruct (03CRS50040).
